---
// components
import Heading from "../../elements/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../../elements/Text.astro";
import Container from "../../elements/Container.astro";
---

<Container variant={'xl'}>
    <Heading tagName="h2" tagSize="h2" class="text-center">About</Heading>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 text-base-900 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <Text variant={'xl'}>We're a small, independent app studio that builds interesting apps and games for iOS and Android.</Text>
        <Text variant={'sm'}>At Danger Apps, we believe the best ideas come from curiosity and a willingness to experiment. We're a tight-knit team that loves building things people actually want to use — whether that's a quick daily puzzle to brighten your commute or a tool that solves a real problem in a fresh way.</Text>
        <Text variant={'sm'}>We keep things simple: small team, big ideas, quality over quantity. Every app we ship is something we'd want on our own phones.</Text>
    </div>
</Container>
